T1  - Determinants of Risky Decision-Making Behavior: A Test of the Mediating Role of Risk Perceptions and Propensity
AU  - Sitkin, Sim B.
AU  - Weingart, Laurie R.
Y1  - 1995/12/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/12/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/256844
